"Abstract FAS stands for the American Federation of Scientists and luckily, among their many interests and concerns is Information Warfare and Information Security on the Web ( www.fas.org/irp/wwwinfo.html ). Lucky for us the lonely punters that is, because we need expert resources pooled in a meaningful and accessible way. And that is exactly the role this meta page fulfils. It is a comprehensive guide to information warfare resources on the Web, as well as a directory of points of entry to related resources."
